name: Five Nights at Obama's
description:
Five Nights at Obama's is a parody of Five Nights at Freddy's created by Scott Cawthon. This project is being made with me and my friends as a fun side project. Currently, this won't be made as a game. But, it might be in the future. This page is to help people stay informed on the updates of the project.
